content: Season 1 was the best but season 3 was the worst.  What's the matter, was Zoom too scary for you lol.
All 3 seasons were amazing.  Maybe I'm biased.
I think I picked up on some comments that might refer to tweeting that I thought had some political meaning but other than that I thought it was great.
I don't think it was too political but it did have some undertones and efforts suggesting a more modern ideology in politics.
Trying to find peace among existing aliens on earth and integrating them had some signs of recognition of illegal aliens.
I don't think the politics were too much but I can't stand the fact that Jimmy is "The Guardian"!  Since when is he a hero?
It is pretty funny but his humor can get a little too raunchy for me.
Yeah, Sandler can be a little gross.  He definitely has a pubescent sense of humor but it still cracks me up.
Sandler and Spade are like PB&J.  I don't think Vanilla Ice belonged in this movie though.  Rob Schnieder was hilarious as always.
